{
  "stem": "1530.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was a very alert woman who knew politics and everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I still feel that I had something-- I had said the wrong thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know then.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I thought I'm doing my little sister a favor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Let her go with my mother, she is so attached to her.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But then, ever since then, I feel that I killed her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I made her go with my mother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You're so right, but I can't say that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- because I said that she is only 13, I blame myself, 50 years now, that I killed my little sister.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One's mind, when it goes berserk, how can you tell that person how I should feel?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remained with this feeling up until today.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I told my doctor that it doesn't look likely that I am going to get over this.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's been-- actually crippled me all these 50 years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were other things too, but this is the major theme of my illness.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I became a depressive, and seriously depressed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- you know, kind of very active child, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, then they were screaming and yelling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took us into this place where they undressed us, and they put a rag on us, and they take our hair off.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- they-- they shaved our head.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we looked at each other, and we didn't recognize each other.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There may have been Polish or Russian or some kind of people who already were there in Auschwitz--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--Prisoners who did that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But our minds were totally gone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we said this is an insane asylum.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we hardly recognized each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you didn't know where you were.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
